"navVariant":"base","head":{"title":"Making a Will | Moonstone Advocates","description":"Making a Will gives you peace of mind and protects the people and things that matter to you. We'll help you set out exactly what you want to happen to your money, possessions, and property when you die. It's the first step in planning your legacy with our experienced Private Wealth & Succession team.","ogTitle":"Making a Will | Moonstone Advocates","ogDescription":"Making a Will gives you peace of mind and protects the people and things that matter to you. We'll help you set out exactly what you want to happen to your money, possessions, and property when you die. It's the first step in planning your legacy with our experienced Private Wealth & Succession team.","ogType":"website","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","canonical":"making-a-will.html","jsonLd":["{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Making a Will\",\n  \"description\": \"Making a Will gives you peace of mind and protects the people and things that matter to you. We'll help you set out exactly what you want to happen to your money, possessions, and property when you die. It's the first step in planning your legacy with our experienced Private Wealth & Succession team. \",\n  \"url\": \"/for-individuals/private-wealth-succession/making-a-will\",\n  \"inLanguage\": \"en\",\n  \"isPartOf\": {\n    \"@type\": \"WebSite\",\n    \"name\": \"Moonstone Advocates\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.moonstone.co.ug\"\n  },\n  \"about\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Service\",\n    \"name\": \"Making a Will\",\n    \"description\": \"Making a Will gives you peace of mind and protects the people and things that matter to you. We'll help you set out exactly what you want to happen to your money, possessions, and property when you die. It's the first step in planning your legacy with our experienced Private Wealth & Succession team. \",\n    \"provider\": {\n      \"@type\": \"LegalService\",\n      \"name\": \"Moonstone Advocates\",\n      \"department\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Private Wealth & Succession\",\n        \"email\": \"willsandprobateenquiry@moonstone.co.ug\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"serviceType\": \"Private Wealth & Succession\",\n    \"areaServed\": \"GB\"\n  },\n  \"mainEntity\": {\n    \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\n    \"mainEntity\": [\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Can you revisit my old Will from home?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Yes we can revisit old Wills and we can arrange home visits if needed.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"How much does a Will cost? \",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Our fees start at £495 plus VAT for a single Will. We also offer mirror Wills, complex Wills and Inheritance Tax planning options.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"My partner and I are married. We have assets worth more than £325,000, do we need to think about Inheritance Tax planning in our Wills?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Yes, if your assets are above the Nil Rate Band (£325,000), it’s always worth planning ahead to reduce the potential Inheritance Tax burden.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"I’ve heard something about transferring Nil Rate Bands, how does that work?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Since 2007, if you leave your Estate to your spouse or civil partner, the Executors of the surviving partner can also claim the Nil Rate Band of the first to die.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"How much could my partner and I leave without paying Inheritance Tax?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Together, you could leave a combined Estate of £650,000 before inheritance tax becomes payable, anything above this sum will be taxed at 40%.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Are there any other reliefs or allowances we should know about?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Yes, there’s the Residence Nil Rate Band, which can further reduce the inheritance tax due, depending on your circumstances.\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"datePublished\": \"2026-07-09T13:04:22.103Z\",\n  \"dateModified\": \"2026-07-09T13:04:22.103Z\"\n}"]},"blocks":[{"tag":"main","attrs":{"className":"main-wrapper"},"html":"<header data-wf--02-standard-header--variant=\"dark\" data-wf-component-id=\"949280b8-8e72-c6a2-5bfc-7cfb2eeda9b8\" data-wf-variant-state=\"8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\" class=\"section_header w-variant-8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\"><div class=\"padding-global is-page-top\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"simple_header_grid\"><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf8719e-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h1 class=\"heading-style-h1\">Making a Will</h1></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Making a Will gives you peace of mind and protects the people and things that matter to you. We&#x27;ll help you set out exactly what you want to happen to your money, possessions, and property when you die. It&#x27;s the first step in planning your legacy with our experienced Private Wealth &amp; Succession team. </p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" data-btn-hover=\"\" data-theme=\"primary\" href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn is-icon w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Speak to an expert</p></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf871aa-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-right\"><div class=\"simple-header_image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"base\" class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">Home</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/for-individuals\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">For individuals</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Making a Will</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"listing_shape-wrapper w-variant-8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\"><div lottie=\"target-load\" class=\"header_shape is-standard\" data-w-id=\"5d828c84-1f1c-1e38-bfb3-80ffb8d04940\" data-animation-type=\"lottie\" data-src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69db9824cf9ff19dd03c1c29_08fdbca2c62ae345f765f433c8401fe4_Moonstone_V_Blue.json\" data-loop=\"0\" data-direction=\"1\" data-autoplay=\"1\" data-is-ix2-target=\"0\" data-renderer=\"svg\" data-default-duration=\"0\" data-duration=\"0\" data-loading=\"lazy\"></div></div><div class=\"simple-header_background-image-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-overlay-layer\"></div><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_background-image\"></div></header><section class=\"section_benefit-grid_layout\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid benefit-grid_list\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Choose who looks after your children </h4><p>Your Will lets you name the people you trust to care for your children if you&#x27;re no longer here. Without it, the courts decide. We&#x27;ll help you make a plan that puts their care and security first.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Set out your funeral wishes </h4><p>You can use your Will to express your preferences for your funeral. Whether you want something simple, personal or specific, we’ll make sure your wishes are clearly recorded.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Leave gifts to people and charities </h4><p>Whether it’s a cash sum, a sentimental item or support for a cause close to your heart, your Will lets you leave gifts that reflect your values and your relationships.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Decide who inherits your estate </h4><p>If you don’t have a Will, your estate is divided by strict legal rules that don’t always reflect modern families. We’ll help you choose how everything you leave is shared, fairly and clearly.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Plan for Inheritance Tax </h4><p>With the right structure, your Will can help reduce Inheritance Tax. We&#x27;ll advise you on how best to use tax-free allowances and protect more of your estate for the people you care about.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Support blended families </h4><p>If you or your partner have children from previous relationships, we’ll help you strike the right balance. We can structure your Will so everyone you love is protected, fairly.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Thinking ahead</h4><p>A Will sets out what should happen to your estate after your death, but your executors may also need to obtain Probate before they can administer your estate. We can advise on both Wills and Probate, helping to ensure your affairs are dealt with efficiently and in accordance with your wishes.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_accordion\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"faq6_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid faq6_content\"><div class=\"faq6_content-left\"><h2>Questions we’re often asked</h2><div class=\"margin-top margin-small\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"button is-secondary w-button\">Speak to an expert</a></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_list\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid faq6_list-grid\"><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f7d\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Can you revisit my old Will from home?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Yes we can revisit old Wills and we can arrange home visits if needed.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f88\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>How much does a Will cost? </div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Our fees start at £495 plus VAT for a single Will. We also offer mirror Wills, complex Wills and Inheritance Tax planning options.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f93\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>My partner and I are married. We have assets worth more than £325,000, do we need to think about Inheritance Tax planning in our Wills?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Yes, if your assets are above the Nil Rate Band (£325,000), it’s always worth planning ahead to reduce the potential Inheritance Tax burden.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f9e\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>I’ve heard something about transferring Nil Rate Bands, how does that work?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Since 2007, if you leave your Estate to your spouse or civil partner, the Executors of the surviving partner can also claim the Nil Rate Band of the first to die.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7fa9\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>How much could my partner and I leave without paying Inheritance Tax?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Together, you could leave a combined Estate of £650,000 before inheritance tax becomes payable, anything above this sum will be taxed at 40%.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"0a8deace-1e08-c9a3-2888-1d317fe93eb6\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Are there any other reliefs or allowances we should know about?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Yes, there’s the Residence Nil Rate Band, which can further reduce the inheritance tax due, depending on your circumstances.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone provided an excellent, comprehensive service when drawing up my will and Lasting Power Attorney. Emily Owston was professional and answered all of my questions.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Black Solicitors LLP. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using Moonstone, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I find this practice gives clients individual attention as needed. I can only speak for myself, but they have given me everything I asked for and advice when they felt it was needed. They have made me feel that they understand my problems and give me advice on how to deal with them.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Members of the team we have met are professional, friendly and knowledgeable, giving a tailor-made personal service making suggestions that are unique to our requirements.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Each member of the team I have come into contact with has been lovely &amp; they often go that extra mile to get the job done with the least inconvenience to myself &amp; other family members. They show care, sensitivity &amp; are very supportive. Nothing seems to be too much trouble.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very personal service, made to feel comfortable and supported. The confidence we felt in the advice given was second to none. Everything is explained at every step of the process.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I have been with Moonstone Advocates for many years and have nothing but praise for them. Without exception whoever has dealt with our legal issues &amp; requirements has been professional &amp; efficient, as well as sensitive &amp; supportive.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_team\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"slider-main_component\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-4-card-slider\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_instance\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Experts in every area</h2><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div hover-zoom=\"trigger\" class=\"team-member_item\"><a href=\"/our-people/sophie-balfour\" class=\"team-member_item w-inline-block\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"team-member_image-wrapper\"><img hover-zoom=\"target\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b44ab164a8844c96471e18/6a1ef9b78c0e916d5fffd2e6_695d215c57c1a0f9462699b5_Moonstone-JMA-PHOTOGRAPHY-DSC_3788%2520-low-res.jpeg\" class=\"image is-team\"></div></div><div class=\"team-member_text-wrapper\"><div fs-list-field=\"full-name\" class=\"text-size-large text-weight-semibold\">Sophie Balfour</div><div class=\"hidden-text\"><div fs-list-field=\"first-name\">Sophie</div><div fs-list-field=\"last-name\" class=\"text-size-large text-weight-semibold\">Balfour</div></div><div class=\"article-meta\"><div fs-list-field=\"job-title\" class=\"secondary_tag\">Paralegal</div></div></div></a></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-4-card-slide